00:11:52.566 --> 00:11:54.795
Radi jos nesto veoma vazno.

00:11:54.795 --> 00:11:57.639
Posjeduje jednostavan interfejs za korisnike.

00:11:57.639 --> 00:12:00.629
Histolog poput mene moze doci,

00:12:00.629 --> 00:12:02.637
staviti cip u kasetu

00:12:02.637 --> 00:12:04.569
poput prototipa kojeg ovdje vidite

00:12:04.569 --> 00:12:06.640
staviti kasetu u masinu

00:12:06.640 --> 00:12:08.128
kao sto biste vi stavili CD,

00:12:08.128 --> 00:12:09.260
i to je to.

00:12:09.260 --> 00:12:12.009
Ukljuci i pokreni. Jednostavno.

00:12:12.009 --> 00:12:14.523
A sada razmislimo malo

00:12:14.523 --> 00:12:15.902
kakva bi nam mogla biti buducnost

00:12:15.902 --> 00:12:18.315
kada bih mogla uzeti vase maticne celije

00:12:18.315 --> 00:12:19.755
